<p id="p3">SoundSource provides audio control so useful, it ought to be built in to MacOS. Get instant access to your Mac’s audio settings right from the menu bar, with powerful per-app volume and routing control, and the ability to apply effects to any app’s audio.</p>
<p id="p4">The <a href="https://weblog.rogueamoeba.com/2025/12/04/soundsource-6-is-here/" rel="noopener noreferrer">newly released SoundSource 6</a> is a major upgrade, with dozens of enhancements. Updates include supercharged AirPlay support, output groups to send audio to multiple devices at once, Quick Configs that save your entire audio configuration, and a powerful new Audio Devices window that gives deep control over device settings.</p>
